{
  "chapter": 12,
  "chapter_summary": "第十二回\"南宫惊变\"讲述了南宫平与叶曼青在洵阳客栈发现红旗镖局十余名镖师惨死的场景。西河名捕\"金仙奴\"携名犬\"金仙\"前来查案，误认南宫平为凶手。铁戟红旗震中州司马中天赶到，揭穿误会并告知南宫世家正面临重重危难。南宫平与叶曼青逃至堰城郊外武当山脉，意外偷听到\"钱痴\"胁迫武当四木（紫柏、青松、独梧、孤桐道人）交出劫自红旗镖局的南宫世家财物，并得知\"群魔岛\"与七大门派订有密约，要对付南宫世家。梅吟雪与战东来出现，与武当四木交手，叶曼青趁机带南宫平离开。梅吟雪击晕纠缠不休的战东来，与叶曼青同行，暗示她对南宫平的情感。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朋友！振作些！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_biao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "红旗镖客",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "谁？……你是谁？",
      "tone": "虚弱",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_hong_qi_biao_ke",
      "text": "在下南宫平，与贵镖局有旧，只望你将凶手说出……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_biao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "红旗镖客",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "南宫平……南宫……完……了……完了……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_hong_qi_biao_ke",
      "text": "完了！什么完了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_biao_ke",
      "speaker_name": "红旗镖客",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "完了……完……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶曼青",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "南宫……完了……",
      "tone": "沉吟",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶曼青",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "这红旗镖局可是常为你们家护送财物么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_ye_man_qing",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶曼青",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "那么他们这次所护之镖，大约也是南宫世家之物，所以他被人劫镖之后，在惭愧与痛苦之中，才会对你说出这样的话来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶曼青",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "你叹什么气呢？南宫世家即使被人劫走一些财物，也不过有如沧海之一粟，算得了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_ye_man_qing",
      "text": "我哪里会为此叹气。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_ye_man_qing",
      "text": "有些道理极为简单明显之事，我却偏偏要去用最最复杂困难的方法解释，岂非甚是愚蠢？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_xian_nu",
      "speaker_name": "金仙奴",
      "listener": "char_ye_man_qing",
      "text": "那女子快些退后，你难道不要命了么！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_xian_nu",
      "speaker_name": "金仙奴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要生气，不要生气，他们再也不敢碰你的了。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_xian_nu",
      "speaker_name": "金仙奴",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "你两人是谁？还站在这里作甚？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶曼青",
      "listener": "char_jin_xian_nu",
      "text": "我站在这里你管得着么？",
      "tone": "冷然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_xian_nu",
      "speaker_name": "金仙奴",
      "listener": "char_ye_man_qing",
      "text": "好个无知的女子，你可知道我是什么人？竟敢妨害我的公务。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶曼青",
      "listener": "char_jin_xian_nu",
      "text": "我怎么不知道你是什么人，你左右不过是这条小狗的奴才而已。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_xian_nu",
      "speaker_name": "金仙奴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来人呀，替我将这女刁民抓下去！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶曼青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本应狗是人奴，此刻却变了人是狗奴……嘿嘿，嘿嘿。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶曼青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们若有谁敢再前进一步，我立刻便将你们毙在掌下。",
      "tone": "冷然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_xian_nu",
      "speaker_name": "金仙奴",
      "listener": "char_ye_man_qing",
      "text": "真的么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_jin_xian_nu",
      "text": "且慢！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_xian_nu",
      "speaker_name": "金仙奴",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "你是什么人？难道也和这女……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_jin_xian_nu",
      "text": "在下久闻阁下乃是西河名捕，难道连忠奸善恶之分都分不清楚？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_xian_nu",
      "speaker_name": "金仙奴",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "凶杀之场，盗窃之地，岂有忠诚善良之人！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_jin_xian_nu",
      "text": "那么金捕头是否早已认定了在下等不是主谋，便是共犯？在下等在此间，便是专门等着金捕头前来捉拿于我？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_xian_nu",
      "speaker_name": "金仙奴",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "此刻虽尚不能决定，但片刻后便知分晓了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_xian_nu",
      "speaker_name": "金仙奴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金老二，再要麻烦你一次了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_xian_nu",
      "speaker_name": "金仙奴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老二，还没有寻出来么，老二，还没有……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_xian_nu",
      "speaker_name": "金仙奴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄弟们，休要让这两人走了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": "char_ye_man_qing",
      "text": "他若是真的能查出这凶案的凶手，我倒要感激他了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶曼青",
      "listener": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "text": "跟去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "官差",
      "listener": "char_ye_man_qing",
      "text": "哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_xian_nu",
      "speaker_name": "金仙奴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有了我'金仙'的鼻子，还要再查什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "叶曼青轻叱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "畜生！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "沉声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若再不住手，将事情查办清楚，莫怪……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_xian_nu",
      "speaker_name": "金仙奴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，但除了这男女两人之外，似乎还有共谋……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "华服老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说的'凶手'就是他么！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "金仙奴讷讷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "晚辈也不敢深信，但事实……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "华服老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "喊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "走了走了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "惶声接",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "方才我亲眼看到他射出暗器，但不敢说，哪知他乘着……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平微微变色",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么危难？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "叶曼青轻轻",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你留在这里，我去帮着司马老镖头将那人抓回。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "叶曼青茫然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平叹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此事之变化究竟如何，我也猜测不到，但……唉，我此刻但愿能插翅飞回家里……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "叶曼青喜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么，我们快走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "讷讷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "晚辈……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_zhong_tian",
      "speaker_name": "司马中天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这条狗，你也该送回去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_xian_nu",
      "speaker_name": "金仙奴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金仙跟着我十余年，我……我实在……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_zhong_tian",
      "speaker_name": "司马中天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咳，这孩子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "干咳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄兄、凌兄……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_zhong_tian",
      "speaker_name": "司马中天大喝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄兄……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_zhong_tian",
      "speaker_name": "司马中天大声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "极是极是，有些朋友交不交都没有关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_yu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "郭玉霞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "南宫五弟么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_zhong_tian",
      "speaker_name": "司马中天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_zhong_tian",
      "speaker_name": "司马中天大声呼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "平儿，平儿……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_zhong_tian",
      "speaker_name": "司马中天诧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "走了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_yu_xia",
      "speaker_name": "郭玉霞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唉，他到底年纪轻，为了一个声名狼藉的女人，竟不惜犯下众怒，为了梅冷血，他竟将",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "大喝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "任风萍摇头叹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "色字头上一把刀……唉！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "喃喃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "南宫世家已是岌岌可危，他还要如此做法，他还要如此做法……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ma_zhong_tian",
      "speaker_name": "司马中天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "非常之变，非常之变……大厦将倾，大厦将倾……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "喘着气",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "总镖头，不好了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "厉声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "那黑衣劲装的\"红旗镖师\"接口",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "武威、张掖、古浪、永登、新城、兰州六处的八家南宫店铺，一共卖了一百四十万两银子，小的们换成珠宝，方自运到秦安，就……就……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "跺足",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就怎地了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "低语",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人家才不会照顾到这里，我看你们……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 582
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "轻轻",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "堰城快到了吧？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "许多张嘴巴一齐开口",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就在前面。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 592,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道那必定是你心爱的东西，但是我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "轻轻",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你身子还未完全复原，只怕……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "这少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无妨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "翠衫少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你自信可以越过去么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 644,
      "line_end": 644
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "翠衫少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你师门的内功，果然不同凡响。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 648,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "缓缓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但愿天下的富贵人，都能尝一尝贫穷滋味……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 652
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶曼青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你倦了，我们真该好好歇息一下……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 672,
      "line_end": 672
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "讷讷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你没有……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶曼青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两天我吃得太多了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 680,
      "line_end": 680
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "叶曼青一笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难怪那秃头老人会变成财迷钱痴，原来金钱真的重要得很……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 688,
      "line_end": 688
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶曼青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么，他为什么会忽然偷偷跑掉呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 696,
      "line_end": 696
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平苦笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也不知道！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 698,
      "line_end": 698
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "轻轻",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你听这口音像是谁的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 708,
      "line_end": 708
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶曼青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他怎么也到了这里……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 712,
      "line_end": 712
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nan_gong_ping",
      "speaker_name": "南宫平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嘘－－",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 714,
      "line_end": 714
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "方自",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "上面那片山岩如何？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 724,
      "line_end": 724
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "\"钱痴\"",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好极好极，就是上面那片山岩好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 726,
      "line_end": 726
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "坐，请坐。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 738,
      "line_end": 738
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "紫面道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贫道们平生不喜与人玩笑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 740,
      "line_end": 740
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "\"钱痴\"已接口",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "前夜三更……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 752,
      "line_end": 752
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "\"钱痴\"",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "四位道长俱是大智大慧之人，试想我孤身一人，若非早已准备后着，怎敢面对以剑术武功名闻天下的",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 782,
      "line_end": 782
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "紫面道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你纵然说出，却也不会有人相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 786,
      "line_end": 786
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "\"钱痴\"",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此事说来并不十分困难，只要……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 820,
      "line_end": 820
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "\"钱痴\"",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "包在一起。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 850,
      "line_end": 850
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_bai_zhen_ren",
      "speaker_name": "只听\"紫柏道人\"颔首",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 858,
      "line_end": 858
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "\"钱痴\"缓缓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此间除我之外，再无别人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 866,
      "line_end": 866
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_bai_zhen_ren",
      "speaker_name": "紫柏道人缓缓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知若干年前，武林中便已有了'群魔岛'的传说，也不知在若干年前，'群魔岛'便已与……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 878,
      "line_end": 878
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "\"钱痴\"忍不住",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说下去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 888,
      "line_end": 888
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "接",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这密约在少林、昆仑、崆峒、点苍、峨嵋、华山，以及我武当派的掌门人以及有数几个人口中，代代相传，也不知道传了多久，'群魔岛'却始终未曾动过这权力，直到……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 894,
      "line_end": 894
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_bai_zhen_ren",
      "speaker_name": "紫柏道人惊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "南宫平！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 918,
      "line_end": 918
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "惶声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喂……你……你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 926,
      "line_end": 926
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_tong_zhen_ren",
      "speaker_name": "孤桐道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贫道们既不能伤及姑娘，也不能让姑娘下山，只得委屈姑娘，到一个地方去暂住些时日，等到……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 968,
      "line_end": 968
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "齐声叱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 978,
      "line_end": 978
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "山岩下咯咯笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小妹妹！不要怕，是你的老姐姐来了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 980,
      "line_end": 980
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "冷冷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不用你费心，我的事我自己会料理。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 996,
      "line_end": 996
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "\"口中冷冷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我早就要走了！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1028,
      "line_end": 1028
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人家大姑娘要走，你们老道拦住人家做什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1032,
      "line_end": 1032
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_tong_zhen_ren",
      "speaker_name": "孤桐道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1054,
      "line_end": 1054
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "叱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孽障！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1058,
      "line_end": 1058
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_tong_zhen_ren",
      "speaker_name": "孤桐道人冷笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这等身手，也配……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1060,
      "line_end": 1060
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "冷冷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "昆仑门下又怎样？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1066,
      "line_end": 1066
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪咯咯笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么样，我可是没骗你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1086,
      "line_end": 1086
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好不要脸……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1094,
      "line_end": 1094
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶曼青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真的不让我走么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1116,
      "line_end": 1116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_bai_zhen_ren",
      "speaker_name": "紫柏道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为事属敝派一派声誉，贫道不得不如此做了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1118,
      "line_end": 1118
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "举手",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1126,
      "line_end": 1126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_bai_zhen_ren",
      "speaker_name": "紫柏道人沉声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位师弟住手！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1134,
      "line_end": 1134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_bai_zhen_ren",
      "speaker_name": "紫柏道人惶声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "四师弟……你……你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1150,
      "line_end": 1150
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小妹妹，我知道，是你自己走出来的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1170,
      "line_end": 1170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_man_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶曼青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知道便好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1172,
      "line_end": 1172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小妹妹，你要到哪里去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1174,
      "line_end": 1174
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "叶曼青冷冷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你我各行各道，你管我到哪里？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1176,
      "line_end": 1176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "战东来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁愿意管你的事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1178,
      "line_end": 1178
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "轻叱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你少多话！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1182,
      "line_end": 1182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_yin_xue",
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还是让我陪着你们，先医好他的病。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1200,
      "line_end": 1200
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "大声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要跟着他们走么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1202,
      "line_end": 1202
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "战东末变色",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要我走？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1214,
      "line_end": 1214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_dong_lai",
      "speaker_name": "战东来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我什么都告诉了你，什么都给了你，你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1226,
      "line_end": 1226
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "梅吟雪冷冷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么都是你自愿的，难道我曾对你要过什么了？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1228,
      "line_end": 1228
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "突地放声大喊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不能走，我不能离开了你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1230,
      "line_end": 1230
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "喃喃",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "情感……情感……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 1258,
      "line_end": 1258
    }
  ],
